      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six power plant. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and precise VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a limited-slip differential, providing a pure, analog connection to the tarmac. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive cooling system refresh. The chassis retains its signature balance with crisp turn-in and predictable lateral dynamics, making it a superlative example for the discerning driver who prioritizes performance integrity.",
